    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Catalogs of goods available for purchase, to be delivered by the postal service or other delivery service. Orders for the goods may be made by mail, or by another means (such as by telephone).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
